<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Clean1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Clean,</orth> adj., free from dirt or any stain: <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.278" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. III, 1, 278</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 143</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 4.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. IV, 2, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.443" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 443</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.166" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 166</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.1.201" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 1, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.364" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 364</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 49</bibl>. Followed by <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>c. of such filth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.7.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 7, 34</bibl></cit>.
